history.content:
Ryusei Best Hayashi is intending on running for ASUC* Senator and is looking for people to join his campaign team. His vision is to make UC Berkeley be recognized as the best university in the world for the next 10 years consecutively, which shall be remembered in history as “The Berkeley Dynasty.” 

The application closes Feb. 11th. Link: https://tinyurl.com/besthayashiapplication

We are looking for students in the International, Social Entrepreneurship, Environmental Sustainability, and Undergraduate Research communities. https://tinyurl.com/asucobhdescriptions

*Title for identification purposes only
history.subject: Recruiting team for Campaign ASUC Senator* Best Hayashi | Make UC Berkeley the Best University
